299
00:31:35,840 --> 00:31:40,400
I wonder why you've come to the Yan Mansion specifically to see me.

300
00:31:40,400 --> 00:31:44,480
I heard that these past few days, you had repeatedly entered the palace for an audience...

301
00:31:45,120 --> 00:31:47,960
