384
00:37:40,040 --> 00:37:43,240
Eat it up, Sixth Sister. It's still hot.

385
00:37:43,240 --> 00:37:45,080
Thank you, Fourth Sister! Thank you, Fifth Brother!

386
00:37:45,080 --> 00:37:49,360
Sixth Sister, have you been well these days at the Shen Mansion?

387
00:37:49,360 --> 00:37:51,000
I'm fine.

388
00:37:51,000 --> 00:37:52,200
That's good.

389
